N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 8189.18 - Cities, towns and villages

State Regulations

Nothing contained herein shall be construed to preclude a
city, town or village from preparing a proposed tax map for such city, town or
village pursuant to this Part and section
503
of the Real Property Tax
